Description:
  The /FlyCapture2 SDK/ provides c and c++ access to Point Grey (<http://ptgrey.com>) research-grade cameras. 
  The @System.Flycap@ package is limited a binding to the c SDK. Right now in Haskell you can:
  .
    - Get basic system info (camera count, camera manufacturer info)
  .
    - Start/stop acquisition runs
  .
    - Address cameras by index or serial number
  .
    - Set free-running/triggered operation
  .
    - Acquire frames
  .
    - Convert to JuicyPixels types

Source-Repository head
